Second-half goals by Mohamed Yattara and Alexandre Lacazette helped Olympique Lyonnais go top of Ligue
2-0 home win against Bastia on Wednesday
Substitute Yattara opened the scoring in the 77th minute and Ligue
top scorer Lacazette took his tally to 25 eight minutes later to move Lyon up to 64 points from 32 games
Alexandre Lacazette and Mohamed Yattara were both on the score sheet as Lyon beat Bastia
